&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About AppDirect&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Become a digital, global citizen and enable the new generation of digital entrepreneurs around the world.&amp;nbsp; AppDirect offers a subscription commerce platform to sell any product, through any channel, on any device - as a service.&amp;nbsp; We power millions of subscriptions worldwide for organizations.&amp;nbsp; We do this by our values-driven culture—one that enables you to Be Seen, Be Yourself, and Do Your Best Work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a proactive, detail-oriented, and result-driven &lt;strong&gt;Collections Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Finance team. The incumbent will be responsible for managing collections activities, tracking outstanding receivables, following up on overdue accounts, and supporting the organization’s cash flow objectives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate should have hands-on experience in &lt;strong&gt;accounts receivable and collections&lt;/strong&gt;, strong analytical skills, and the confidence to communicate with customers through calls and emails to ensure timely payment follow-ups and resolution of outstanding issues. The candidate should also be proficient in &lt;strong&gt;NetSuite, MS Excel, and Google Sheets&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Manage end-to-end collection activities for assigned customer accounts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Review aging reports and identify overdue invoices/accounts for follow-up.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Follow up with customers through &lt;strong&gt;calls, emails, and other communication channels&lt;/strong&gt; to collect outstanding payments and secure payment commitments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Confidently communicate with customers to address delayed payments and resolve queries related to invoices and balances.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Investigate payment delays, short payments, and disputed invoices in coordination with internal teams such as Finance, Billing, Sales, and Customer Success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Maintain accurate records of collection efforts, customer communication, payment commitments, and follow-up actions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helve

