&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About AppDirect&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Become a digital, global citizen and enable the new generation of digital entrepreneurs around the world. AppDirect offers a subscription commerce platform to sell any product, through any channel, on any device - as a service. We power millions of subscriptions worldwide for organizations. We do this by our values-driven culture - one that enables you to Be Seen, Be Yourself, and Do Your Best Work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;You are a multimedia creative who has embraced AI as a production superpower. You know how to take a creative vision and bring it to life — across video, motion, static, and animation — using the best AI tools available to move faster and reach higher than traditional production allows. You have done this before, you have the work to show for it, and you are ready to build it properly inside a brand that is going through a significant creative and commercial moment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;This is not a role for someone who dabbles in AI on the side. You are fluent across the current generation of AI creative tools, you stay ahead of what is emerging, and you know how to produce output that looks like it belongs to a brand — not just output that looks impressive in isolation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Working directly with the Head of Brand Marketing and in close collaboration with the design team, you will be the production force behind a new demand generation and brand campaigns. You will own the end-to-end creation of AI-assisted marketing assets across every channel including paid ads, TV streaming commercials, social ads, and more.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do and How You’ll Make an Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Campaign Production&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce high-quality AI-assisted creative assets across the full channel mix: Google Ads, Meta Ads, display, carousels, static banners, GIFs, and motion graphics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create demo videos, explainer content, and TV/streaming commercials using AI video generation tools combined with traditional editing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute across multiple formats and aspect ratios simultaneously, maintaining visual consistency and brand fidelity throughout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Iterate quickly based on creative direction, testing feedback, and campaign performance data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Motion, Video &amp;amp; Animation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Drive video and animation production using AI generation tools (Runway, Kling, Hailuo or equivalent) alongside traditional editing in After Effects, Premiere, or equivalent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create motion graphics, animated ads, and short-form video content that serves both performance marketing and brand storytelling goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produce demo and product videos that bring the capabilities of devs.ai and AppDirect to life in compelling, accessible ways&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brand-Consistent AI Workflows&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain prompt systems and generation frameworks that consistently produce on-brand results — not just technically impressive ones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop reusable creative templates and asset libraries that extend the team’s production capacity over time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay ahead of the AI

