&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Customer Success Managers have a unique opportunity to influence PartnerStack customer base and can be a promoter for PartnerStack as well as an advocate for customer needs or gaps in experience.&amp;nbsp; CSMs are essential to a company’s financial growth as they are responsible for growing and transforming customer relationships.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
