&lt;li&gt;Maintain deep knowledge of data center providers, interconnection ecosystems, market pricing, and competitive offerings to support RFPs and multi-site deployments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product, engineering, operations, and provider management teams to validate solution feasibility and align on deployment timelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support contract review and commercial negotiations in partnership with legal and finance teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
