&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;This is a high-impact, high-visibility role for a senior PR professional who wants to own the media narrative for a growing company. As Media Relations Director, you&#39;ll shape and execute our earned media strategy, working directly with executives to land stories in top-tier business and technology outlets. We&#39;re looking for someone with deep journalist relationships, sharp instincts, and the ability to turn company moments into compelling coverage. If you want a seat at the table—not a seat at an agency—this is it.&lt;/p&gt;
