&lt;li&gt;Write and produce all media materials: press releases, pitches, media alerts, bylines, op-eds, briefing docs, talking points, and Q&amp;amp;As&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Brief and prep executives for interviews; provide real-time support during media engagements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor news cycles and identify rapid-response opportunities to insert our POV into relevant conversations&lt;/li&gt;
